{"id": "sos005", "name": "Audio_Sagar_694_06_10", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "Doorbell"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Inhabitant J"], "content": "Coming!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Mrs. James, hello. Got a delivery for you.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Inhabitant J"], "content": "Wah! Such a young delivery boy. Where's Mr. Lee?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "He's in the car. I'm working part-time. Nice to meet you.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Inhabitant J"], "content": "I see. Well, thank you so much. I'm sorry, but this is quite heavy. Can you take it upstairs all by yourself? ...<i>*sigh*</i>... guess he doesn't want to help you out at all.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Ah, no problem. I can do it.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Inhabitant J"], "content": "Looks like Mr. Lee's gotten to that age where he doesn't want to move a muscle, haha. I just need to sign, right?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "That's right. Thanks~\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Inhabitant J"], "content": "Not at all. Send Mr. Lee my regards. If he's ever tough on you, you let me know. \nI'll send in a little complaint to the company, that'll take care of him.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Hahaha... I'm sure that's not necessary. All set. Gotta be going.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Inhabitant J"], "content": "Bye-Bye~\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "Oh, everything go well?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "No problem.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "Haha, Mrs. James is quite a mouthful, eh? Can't stand it.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Haha... she seems nice.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "Kiddo, you work well. Whatta you think? If you can work during the day I'll consider making you full-time; of course, you gotta apply with the Administration Bureau and the Academy.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Oh, sorry. I've got another job in the afternoon...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "Oh? You're really giving it your all. You pressed for cash?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Um, a little, haha...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "Picking up chicks?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Nah, Nah!!! Well, actually...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "I see... you want to apply for the exploration team. Not bad. That being said, I don't even know what they do. Not many kids like you, saving up for something like that. Impressive.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Yeah, but the registration fee is really high. Not sure if I can make it this year.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "Oh? I see what you're doing. You want a raise, eh? No way! What you get is what you get. But, if you're willing to go full time, that's another story!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "I can't... I still need to keep my grades up, the exploration team also has a written test. Plus... I still haven't told my mom that I'm working.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "We're here. We'll talk this over later! No. 53, you got it?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "For sure!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Number 53... Number 53...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Wah!? Mom!? What are you doing here!?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "I'm the one who should be asking you! Didn't you say you were going to your friend's to play? What are you doing wearing these clothes?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Uhh... Umm...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Are you... working!? If you need money you can come to me.\n... <i>*sigh*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "You... you're not still thinking about that, are you? How many times have I told you? That ain't happening!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Mom, please! It's all I want to do! At least let me try!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "No WAY! I'm not gonna let the same thing happen to you that happened to your father!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "You're coming home with me!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Dad's job... maybe it looked dangerous to you, but you never even tried to understand it, did you?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "When I was little, the fondest memories I have of Dad are when he would come home and tell me about everything he saw outside the city walls. To me... they were like fairy tales, but he saw it all with his own eyes.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Dad would speak proudly about that, and that made me proud. He never told you because you were always so worried. You never approved of it. But he told me that never got him down because he knew that what he was doing was for the good of the human race.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "So even if you don't approve, I won't feel bad, and I'm not gonna give up! Because I'm his son.\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "......\nWhatever... fine. Just remember you've got to do well in school...\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "...! Of course!\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "... I'm sorry. I'm just worried about you. But I shouldn't control your life.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "It's not like that...\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "... Plus, you're as dumb as a post, so you're definitely not getting in.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "I... You... What are you saying!? I'll get in, you'll see!\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "I'm going home. Good luck, dummy.\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Damn...\n<font size=\"1.6\">... Thanks, mom.</font>\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "ドアベル"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["住民 J"], "content": "はーい！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Jamesさん、お荷物です。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["住民 J"], "content": "あらまぁ、可愛らしい配達員さんだこと。\nLeeさんはどうしたの？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "車で待ってます。\n俺はバイトです。はじめまして。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["住民 J"], "content": "あら、そうなの。お疲れ様。\n悪いわね、こんな重いもの……一人でここまで運んできたの？\nもう！手伝ってもらえばよかったのに。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "あ、大丈夫ですよ。\n俺一人で運べます。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["住民 J"], "content": "Leeさんもサボりたいお年頃なのかしら？ふふ。\nサインすればいいのかしら？ \n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "はい。ありがとうございます。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["住民 J"], "content": "いいえ、Leeさんによろしくね。\nいじわるされたら私に言いなさい。\n代わりにクレーム入れてあげるから。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "ははは……大丈夫ですよ。\nはい、これで大丈夫です。では失礼します。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["住民 J"], "content": "じゃあね～\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "おっ、平気だったか？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "はい。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "Jamesさん話長いだろ？\nだから行きたくないんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "すごく……情熱的？な方でした。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "チビ、やるじゃねぇか。\nどうだ？もし昼間もシフトに入れるってんなら、正社員にしてやってもいいぞ。\nま、管理局とアカデミーの許可が下りればの話だけどな。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "あ、すみません……午後は他の仕事があって……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "へぇ？頑張るねぇ。\n金に困ってんのか？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "えっと……はい、少しだけ……はは……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "女か？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "ち、違います！実は……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "なるほどねぇ……探査隊に志願したいと。\nいいんじゃねぇーの？\nあいつらが何をしてんのかはイマイチ分かんねぇけどよ、お前みたいに目標のために金を稼ぐって若者はめっきり減っちまったからな。\n俺は好きだぜ。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "はい。\nでも探査隊の受験料が結構高くて……今年は間に合うかどうか……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "ん？なんだ？\nそれはあれか？暗に給料上げろって言ってんのか？\nダメダメ！給料は上げないぞ！\nま、正社員になるってんならまた話は別だけどよ。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "それは本当に無理なんですって……\nアカデミーの成績だって落とすわけにはいかないし、探査隊の入試も筆記テストがあるんですから。\nそれに……実は母親に言ってないんです。バイトのこと。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "ついたぞー。話の続きはまた後でな！\n53番、行けるか？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "はい！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "53……53……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "？\nうわ！？母さん！？\nなんでこんなところに！？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "そんなのこっちが聞きたいわよ。\nお友達の家に遊びに行くって言ってなかった？\nその格好はなに？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "あ……それは……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "まさか……バイトでもしてるの？\nお金が必要ならお母さんが……あっ……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "あなた……まさかまだあんなバカげたことを考えてるんじゃないでしょうね？\n何があってもそれだけはダメって言ったはずでしょう！？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……母さん！\nこれは俺の唯一の目標であって、唯一やりたいことなんだ！\nお願いだよ……挑戦させてほしい。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "ダメよ！\nあなたにはお父さんみたいに危険な仕事はさせません！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "帰るわよ！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "父さんの仕事は……母さんにとっては「危険」なだけの仕事だったかもしれない。\nでも……母さんは少しでも知ろうとしたことはある？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "父さんが生きてた頃、父さんは家に帰ってくるたびに町の外で起こった出来事について教えてくれた。\n子供の俺にとっては、まるで……童話みたいだった。\nでも、あれは童話なんかじゃない。父さんが実際に経験した事実なんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "父さんはいつも誇らしげに話してくれた。\n父さんが母さんに話さなかったのは、母さんは心配するばかりで、ちゃんと父さんを見てあげてなかったからだ。\nでも、父さんはだからと言って気を落とすことはなかった。\nだって、父さんは自分の仕事が人類の役に立ってるって信じてたから。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "だから、母さんに反対されても俺は動じない。\n諦めない！\nだって、俺は父さんの息子だから。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "………\n勝手に……しなさい。\nアカデミーにはちゃんと行くのよ……\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "！\nもちろん！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……ごめんなさい。\nお母さんは……ただあなたが心配なの。\nでも、だからといってあなたの人生を思い通りにしていいわけがないわよね。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "いいよ……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……でも、あなたのその三歩歩くと忘れるニワトリ頭じゃ、受かりっこないわよ。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "え……ちょ、母さん！\n絶対受かってみせるからな！\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "お母さんは先に帰ってるわね。\n頑張りなさい。ニワトリ頭さん。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "くっそー……\n<font size=\"1.6\">……母さん、ありがとう。</font>\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "門鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "來了！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "James 小姐，您好，送貨。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "哎呀，好年輕的小送貨員。Lee 先生呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "他在車上，我是打工的。妳好。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "這樣啊，辛苦你了。真不好意思，這麼重的東西，你一個人搬上來嗎？真是的，他也不幫個忙。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊，不會啦，我搬得動。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "Lee 先生也到了想偷懶的年紀呢，哈哈。\n一樣這邊簽名就好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "對的，謝謝妳喔。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "不會，幫我跟 Lee 先生問好。如果被他壓榨了要讓我知道喔，我會幫你投訴他的。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哈哈哈……應該不會吧。那這樣就可以了，我先走了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "拜拜～\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "喔，還順利嗎？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "沒問題。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "哈哈，James 小姐話很多對吧？所以我才不想上去。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哈哈……她很熱情。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "小子，你幹得不錯。怎樣？要是白天也能排班的話我可以考慮讓給你全職；當然要跟管理局和學院申請過啦。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊，抱歉，我下午有別的工要打了……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "喔？真拼啊。很缺錢嗎？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "嗯，有一點，哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "把妹嗎？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不、不是啦！其實……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "這樣啊……你想報考探勘隊。不錯啊，雖然不太清楚他們是幹啥的。現在年輕人很少有像你這種因為目標努力賺錢的人了，我欣賞。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "嗯，不過報名費蠻貴的，不知道我趕不趕得上今年的……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "喔？這是在暗示加薪嗎？不行不行！工資就是這樣，不過如果你願意做全職的話就另當別論啦！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "真的不行啦……還有學院的成績要顧，探勘隊的考試也是有筆試的。而且……我還沒告訴我媽我在打工的事。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "到了，等等再聊吧！\n53 號，你行吧？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "好！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "53 號……53 號……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "？\n哇！？媽！？妳怎麼在這裡！？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "我才要問你，你不是說去同學家玩嗎？穿成這樣是在幹嘛？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊……呃……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "你……在偷打工嗎？需要錢可以跟媽媽借啊……啊……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "你……該不會還在想那件事吧？我不是說了不准了嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……媽，拜託了！這是我現在唯一有目標跟動力做的事！妳讓我試試看吧？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "不行！我不會讓你跟你爸爸一樣去做那種危險的工作！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "馬上跟我回家！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "爸爸的工作……可能在妳眼裡只有危險，但是妳從來沒有去了解過吧？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "小時候我對爸最深的記憶，就是他每次回家的時候，說著在城外遭遇到的一切。那些對我來說……就好像童話故事一樣，但都是他的親身經歷。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "爸總是一臉驕傲地說著那些事，讓我也覺得好驕傲。他沒有跟妳說這些，是因為妳只會一直擔心，沒有真正肯定過他。但他跟我說過，他從來沒有因為這樣而感到沮喪，因為他相信自己在做的是對人類有貢獻的事情。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "所以就算妳反對，我也不會沮喪，也不會放棄的！因為我是他兒子。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……。\n隨便……隨便你吧。記得學院還是要好好去就好……\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "！\n當然！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……對不起，我真的很擔心你。但我也不該操控你的人生。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不會……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……反正你這個豬腦袋，一定考不上的。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "妳、妳說什麼啊！？我就考上給妳看！\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "我要回家了，你就好好加油吧，豬腦袋。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "可惡……\n<font size=\"1.6\">……媽，謝了。</font>\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "도어벨"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["주민 J"], "content": "왔다!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "James 씨, 안녕하세요. 물건 도착했습니다.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["주민 J"], "content": "어머~ 이렇게 젊은 분이 배달원이라니, Lee 씨는요?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "차에 있습니다. 저는 아르바이트로 나왔어요. \n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["주민 J"], "content": "그렇구나. 고생이 많네요. 정말 미안해요. 이렇게 무거운데 혼자 옮길 수 있겠어요? 에휴, 그 사람도 조금 도와주면 어디 덧나나?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아, 괜찮습니다.\n혼자서 옮길 수 있습니다.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["주민 J"], "content": "Lee 씨도 슬슬 게으름 피울 수 있는 짬밥이 됐나 봐요? 하하하. \n여기에 사인하면 돼죠?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "네, 감사합니다.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["주민 J"], "content": "아니에요. Lee 씨한테도 안부 전해주세요. 그리고 만약에 계속 힘든 일 시키고 그러면 저한테 말해줘요. 회사에다가 확 찔러버릴 테니까.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "히히히......괜찮습니다. \n아, 이제 됐습니다. 먼저 가보겠습니다.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["주민 J"], "content": "조심히 가요~\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "잘 처리했어?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "문제없습니다.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "하하하, James 씨 말 엄청 많지?\n내가 괜히 차에 있던 게 아니라고.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "하하하.....확실히 에너지가 넘치시는 분 같더군요.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "아주 잘 했어, 애송이.\n만약에 낮에도 이 일하겠다면 정규직 전환도 고려해줄 수 있는데, 어때? 물론 관리국과 아카데미에 허가는 받아 놔야지.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아, 죄송합니다... 오후에는 다른 아르바이트가 있어서...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "뭐? 완전 부지런하구먼!\n돈이 부족하기라도 한 거야?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아, 네.... 조금.... 하하하....\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "여자라도 꼬시려고?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아, 아닙니다! 사실은...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "그렇군......탐사대에 지원하고 싶다니, 그것도 나쁘지 않지. 뭐, 그 녀석들이 무슨 일을 하는지는 정확히 모르겠지만 말이야. 요즘 젊은 사람들 중에선 너처럼 이렇게 목표를 가지고 열심히 돈을 벌려고 하는 놈들은 거의 보질 못했어. 꽤 인상 깊군.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "네. 어쨌든 신청비가 조금 비싸서... 올해 시험은 신청할 수 있을지...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "응?\n지금 은근슬쩍 돈 올려달라는 얘기하는 거 아니지?\n아이고, 안 돼, 안 돼! 그 이상 주는 건 힘들어. 그래도 만약 정규직 생각이 있다면 얘기는 또 다르지만 말이야!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "그건 정말로 무리에요.... 아카데미 성적도 관리해야 하고 탐사대 시험에는 필기시험도 있어서. 그리고... 아르바이트하는 사실 아직 엄마한테도 말씀을 못 드렸어요.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "도착했다. 나중에 다시 얘기하고, \n53호, 할 수 있지?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "네!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "53호......53호......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar? \n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "? \n으앗!? 엄마!? \n엄마가 왜 여기에 있어요!?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "나야말로 묻고 싶구나. 친구 집에 놀러 간다면서? 그 옷차림은 또 뭐고? \n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아... 그게.....\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "너 혹시......아르바이트하니? 돈이 필요하면 엄마한테 말하지 그랬어... 하아...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "설마 너......그 일 때문에 그러니? 엄마가 허락 못 한다고 했지!?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": ".....엄마, 제발요! \n그게 제 유일한 목표이자 꿈이라고요! \n한번 도전이라도 해볼 수 있게...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "안 돼! \n네 아빠처럼 너까지 그런 위험한 일을 하게 그냥 둘 순 없어!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "당장 집으로 돌아가자꾸나!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아빠가 하던 일이......엄마 눈에는 그저 위험한 일로만 보이겠지만, 한 번도 제대로 이해해보려고 한 적은 없잖아요?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "......! \n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "어렸을 적, 아버지가 매번 집에 돌아오실 때마다 도시 바깥에서 일어났던 일들을 제게 말씀해주신 기억이 나요. 그때 그 기억은 제게 있어서... 마치 동화와 같은 이야기들이었어요. 하지만 그것들은 결코 동화가 아니었죠. 아버지가 몸소 체험하셨던 일들이었어요.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아버지는 항상 그러한 이야기를 아주 자랑스러운 듯이 제게 말해주시곤 하셨어요. 엄마한테 말하지 않은 이유는 엄마는 그저 걱정할 뿐, 제대로 아버지를 봐주지 않아서였을 거예요. 하지만 그렇다고 해서 아버지는 낙심해하시지도 않으셨어요. 줄곧 자신이 인류를 위한 일을 행하고 있다고 믿고 계셨으니까요.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "......! \n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "그러니까 엄마가 반대를 한다고 해도, 전 낙심하지 않을 거고 포기하지도 않을 거예요! 전 아버지의 아들이니까!\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "......\n마음대로......네 마음대로 하려무나. 그래도 아카데미는 제대로 졸업하도록 해....\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "! \n물론이죠!\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "......미안하구나. 엄마도 네가 너무 걱정돼서 한 말이지만 그렇다고 네가 결정한 진로를 내 멋대로 간섭할 수도 없는 노릇이구나.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아니에요......\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "......어쨌든 너 같은 돌대가리로는 한 번에 시험에 붙을 일도 없겠지.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "뭐.... 뭐라고요!? \n반드시 붙을 거예요! 붙나 안 붙나 지켜보시라고요!\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "엄마는 집에 가야겠구나. 힘내거라, 돌대가리.\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "쳇......\n<font size=\"1.6\">......엄마... 고마워요.</font>\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "門鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "來了！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "James 小姐，您好，送貨。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "哎呀，好年輕的小送貨員。Lee 先生呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "他在車上，我是打工的。妳好。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "這樣啊，辛苦你了。真不好意思，這麼重的東西，你一個人搬上來嗎？真是的，他也不幫個忙。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊，不會啦，我搬得動。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "Lee 先生也到了想偷懶的年紀呢，哈哈。\n一樣這邊簽名就好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "對的，謝謝妳喔。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "不會，幫我跟 Lee 先生問好。如果被他壓榨了要讓我知道喔，我會幫你投訴他的。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哈哈哈……應該不會吧。那這樣就可以了，我先走了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "拜拜～\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "喔，還順利嗎？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "沒問題。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "哈哈，James 小姐話很多對吧？所以我才不想上去。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哈哈……她很熱情。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "小子，你幹得不錯。怎樣？要是白天也能排班的話我可以考慮讓給你全職；當然要跟管理局和學院申請過啦。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊，抱歉，我下午有別的工要打了……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "喔？真拼啊。很缺錢嗎？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "嗯，有一點，哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "把妹嗎？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不、不是啦！其實……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "這樣啊……你想報考探勘隊。不錯啊，雖然不太清楚他們是幹啥的。現在年輕人很少有像你這種因為目標努力賺錢的人了，我欣賞。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "嗯，不過報名費蠻貴的，不知道我趕不趕得上今年的……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "喔？這是在暗示加薪嗎？不行不行！工資就是這樣，不過如果你願意做全職的話就另當別論啦！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "真的不行啦……還有學院的成績要顧，探勘隊的考試也是有筆試的。而且……我還沒告訴我媽我在打工的事。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "到了，等等再聊吧！\n53 號，你行吧？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "好！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "53 號……53 號……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "？\n哇！？媽！？妳怎麼在這裡！？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "我才要問你，你不是說去同學家玩嗎？穿成這樣是在幹嘛？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊……呃……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "你……在偷打工嗎？需要錢可以跟媽媽借啊……啊……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "你……該不會還在想那件事吧？我不是說了不准了嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……媽，拜託了！這是我現在唯一有目標跟動力做的事！妳讓我試試看吧？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "不行！我不會讓你跟你爸爸一樣去做那種危險的工作！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "馬上跟我回家！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "爸爸的工作……可能在妳眼裡只有危險，但是妳從來沒有去了解過吧？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "小時候我對爸最深的記憶，就是他每次回家的時候，說著在城外遭遇到的一切。那些對我來說……就好像童話故事一樣，但都是他的親身經歷。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "爸總是一臉驕傲地說著那些事，讓我也覺得好驕傲。他沒有跟妳說這些，是因為妳只會一直擔心，沒有真正肯定過他。但他跟我說過，他從來沒有因為這樣而感到沮喪，因為他相信自己在做的是對人類有貢獻的事情。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "所以就算妳反對，我也不會沮喪，也不會放棄的！因為我是他兒子。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……。\n隨便……隨便你吧。記得學院還是要好好去就好……\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "！\n當然！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……對不起，我真的很擔心你。但我也不該操控你的人生。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不會……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……反正你這個豬腦袋，一定考不上的。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "妳、妳說什麼啊！？我就考上給妳看！\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "我要回家了，你就好好加油吧，豬腦袋。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "可惡……\n<font size=\"1.6\">……媽，謝了。</font>\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "门铃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "来了！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "James 小姐，您好，送货。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "哎呀，好年轻的小送货员。 Lee 先生呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "他在车上，我是打工的。妳好。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "这样啊，辛苦你了。真不好意思，这么重的东西，你一个人搬上来吗？真是的，他也不帮个忙。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊，不会啦，我搬得动。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "Lee 先生也到了想偷懒的年纪呢，哈哈。\n一样这边签名就好吗？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "对的，谢谢妳喔。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "不会，帮我跟 Lee 先生问好。如果被他压榨了要让我知道喔，我会帮你投诉他的。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哈哈哈……应该不会吧。那这样就可以了，我先走了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民 J"], "content": "拜拜～\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "喔，还顺利吗？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "没问题。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "哈哈，James 小姐话很多对吧？所以我才不想上去。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哈哈……她很热情。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "小子，你干得不错。怎样？要是白天也能排班的话我可以考虑让给你全职；当然要跟管理局和学院申请过啦。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊，抱歉，我下午有别的工要打了……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "喔？真拼啊。很缺钱吗？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "嗯，有一点，哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "把妹吗？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不、不是啦！其实……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "这样啊……你想报考探勘队。不错啊，虽然不太清楚他们是干啥的。现在年轻人很少有像你这种因为目标努力赚钱的人了，我欣赏。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "嗯，不过报名费蛮贵的，不知道我赶不赶得上今年的……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "喔？这是在暗示加薪吗？不行不行！工资就是这样，不过如果你愿意做全职的话就另当别论啦！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "真的不行啦……还有学院的成绩要顾，探勘队的考试也是有笔试的。而且……我还没告诉我妈我在打工的事。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lee"], "content": "到了，等等再聊吧！\n53 号，你行吧？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "好！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "53 号……53 号……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "？\n哇！ ？妈！ ？妳怎么在这里！ ？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "我才要问你，你不是说去同学家玩吗？穿成这样是在干嘛？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊……呃……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "你……在偷打工吗？需要钱可以跟妈妈借啊……啊……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "你……该不会还在想那件事吧？我不是说了不准了吗！ ？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……妈，拜托了！这是我现在唯一有目标跟动力做的事！妳让我试试看吧？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "不行！我不会让你跟你爸爸一样去做那种危险的工作！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "马上跟我回家！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "爸爸的工作……可能在妳眼里只有危险，但是妳从来没有去了解过吧？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "小时候我对爸最深的记忆，就是他每次回家的时候，说着在城外遭遇到的一切。那些对我来说……就好像童话故事一样，但都是他的亲身经历。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "爸总是一脸骄傲地说着那些事，让我也觉得好骄傲。他没有跟妳說这些，是因为妳只会一直担心，没有真正肯定过他。但他跟我说过，他从来没有因为这样而感到沮丧，因为他相信自己在做的是对人类有贡献的事情。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "所以就算妳反对，我也不会沮丧，也不会放弃的！因为我是他儿子。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……。\n随便……随便你吧。记得学院还是要好好去就好……\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "！\n当然！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……对不起，我真的很担心你。但我也不该操控你的人生。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不会……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "……反正你这个猪脑袋，一定考不上的。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "妳、妳說什么啊！ ？我就考上给妳看！\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "我要回家了，你就好好加油吧，猪脑袋。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "可恶……\n<font size=\"1.6\">……妈，谢了。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}